#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:10
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:10:DefaultText"
msgid "Stand down, all of you. We're done here."
msgstr "Všichni ustupte. Tady jsme skončili."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:11
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:11:DefaultText"
msgid "You want to know what gets my bile churning?"
msgstr "Chcete vědět, co mi hýbe žlučí?"

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:15
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:15:DefaultText"
msgid "Edgewater has suffered a cavalcade of disasters. Plague. Marauders. Desertion. Then you wandered in town, and I was so damn sure our luck was starting to turn."
msgstr "Edgewater postihla celá řada katastrof. Mor. Nájezdníci. Dezerce. Pak ses zatoulal do města ty a já si byl zatraceně jistý, že se na nás začíná lepit štěstí."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:17
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:17:DefaultText"
msgid "I never knew how right I was. Just answer one question for me - why'd you do it? "
msgstr "Nikdy jsem netušil, jak moc jsem měl pravdu. Jen mi odpověz na jednu otázku - proč jsi to udělal? "

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:19
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:19:DefaultText"
msgid "It's not personal. I need your power regulator."
msgstr "Není to osobní. Potřebuji tvůj regulátor výkonu."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:20
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:20:DefaultText"
msgid "I don't owe you an explanation."
msgstr "Nedlužím ti žádné vysvětlení."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:21
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:21:DefaultText"
msgid "You're a horrible person, and you deserve everything that's coming to you."
msgstr "Jsi hrozný člověk a zasloužíš si všechno, co tě čeká."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:22
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:22:DefaultText"
msgid "I see. All right, then. Glad you got that off your chest."
msgstr "Chápu. Dobře tedy. Jsem rád, že jste to ze sebe dostal."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:23
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:23:DefaultText"
msgid "Whatever you were hoping to find down here, I advise you to turn around and leave. I have got guards posted, with orders to fire on you."
msgstr "Ať už jsi doufal, že tady dole najdeš cokoli, radím ti, aby ses otočil a odešel. Mám tu stráže s rozkazem na vás střílet."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:24
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:24:DefaultText"
msgid "That power regulator is company property."
msgstr "Tento regulátor výkonu je majetkem společnosti."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:25
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:25:DefaultText"
msgid "You're right. I put the fate of our town in the hands of some feckless transient. This is my fault, and all Edgewater's paying for my mistake."
msgstr "Máte pravdu. Vložil jsem osud našeho města do rukou nějakého bezohledného přechodného obyvatele. Je to moje chyba a celý Edgewater za ni platí."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:26
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:26:DefaultText"
msgid "Call off your guards. I don't want them bleeding all over my power regulator."
msgstr "Odvolejte stráže. Nechci, aby mi krváceli po celém regulátoru výkonu."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:27
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:27:DefaultText"
msgid "I'm leaving."
msgstr "Odcházím."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:28
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:28:DefaultText"
msgid "I'm sorry about all this, Reed."
msgstr "Je mi to všechno líto, Reede."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:30
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:30:DefaultText"
msgid "What's going to happen to Edgewater?"
msgstr "Co se stane s Edgewaterem?"

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:31
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:31:DefaultText"
msgid "To teach you a lesson."
msgstr "Aby ti dal lekci."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:32
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:32:DefaultText"
msgid "Is that right? I'm dying to hear this. Please. Educate me."
msgstr "Je to tak? Umírám touhou to slyšet. Prosím. Pouč mě."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:36
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:36:DefaultText"
msgid "You're all slaves to Spacer's Choice. I'm liberating you."
msgstr "Všichni jste otroky Spacer's Choice. Osvobozuji vás."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:37
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:37:DefaultText"
msgid "Adelaide had the right idea. I had to make you see that."
msgstr "Adelaide měla správný nápad. Musela jsem ti to vysvětlit."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:38
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:38:DefaultText"
msgid "Life is full of betrayals. I'm just the most recent one."
msgstr "Život je plný zrad. Já jsem jen tou nejnovější."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:39
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:39:DefaultText"
msgid "That may be the most honest thing you have said to me."
msgstr "To je možná ta nejupřímnější věc, kterou jsi mi řekl."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:40
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:40:DefaultText"
msgid "Liberating? Edgewater is my home. The only home I've ever had. I put down roots here. Gave decades of my life to this place. I never asked to be liberated."
msgstr "Osvobozující? Edgewater je můj domov. Jediný domov, který jsem kdy měl. Zapustil jsem zde kořeny. Obětoval jsem tomuto místu desítky let svého života. Nikdy jsem nežádal o osvobození."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:41
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:41:DefaultText"
msgid "Adelaide? Adelaide wants nothing more than to see this town suffer. To see me suffer. All you've done is satisfied her hatred."
msgstr "Adelaide? Adelaide si nepřeje nic jiného, než aby toto město trpělo. Vidět mě trpět. Všechno, co jsi udělal, je uspokojení její nenávisti."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:42
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:42:DefaultText"
msgid "Apologies won't give us our lives back. But, for what it is worth? I am sorry, too."
msgstr "Omluvy nám život nevrátí. Ale ať to stojí, co to stojí. I já se omlouvám."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:43
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:43:DefaultText"
msgid "Edgewater's dead. Our cannery's dead. Adelaide's deserters are never coming back."
msgstr "Edgewater je mrtvý. Naše konzervárna je mrtvá. Dezertéři z Adelaide se už nikdy nevrátí."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:44
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:44:DefaultText"
msgid "Spacer's Choice will shut us down before long. Some of us will die of illness by then. Some will move on. Some will starve."
msgstr "Spacer's Choice nás zanedlouho zavře. Někteří z nás do té doby zemřou na nemoci. Někteří půjdou dál. Někteří zemřou hlady."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:45
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:45:DefaultText"
msgid "I'll order my guards to stand down. Take what you came for, and then leave us be."
msgstr "Nařídím svým strážím, aby se stáhly. Vezměte si, pro co jste přišli, a pak nás nechte být."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:47
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:47:DefaultText"
msgid "You and I have got nothing more to say to each other."
msgstr "My dva si už nemáme co říct."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:48
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:48:DefaultText"
msgid "Dunno. I like pressing buttons, I guess."
msgstr "Nevím. Asi rád mačkám tlačítka."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:49
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:49:DefaultText"
msgid "Wonderful. Law have mercy. Well done, Reed. You went and delivered the fate of Edgewater into the hands of a certified imbecile."
msgstr "Nádhera. Zákon se slituje. Dobrá práce, Reede. Šel jsi a vydal osud Edgewateru do rukou certifikovaného imbecila."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:50
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:50:DefaultText"
msgid "And as for me - I will tender my resignation. Whereupon I shall be processed. And then duly imprisoned for gross incompetence."
msgstr "A pokud jde o mě - podávám rezignaci. Poté budu zpracován. A pak budu řádně uvězněn za hrubou neschopnost."

#: conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:51
msgctxt "conversations/00_emerald_vale/00_cv_reed_confrontation:51:DefaultText"
msgid "All right. Easy now. Let's not do anything we'll regret."
msgstr "Dobře. Teď už je to snadné. Neudělejme nic, čeho bychom litovali."